highlights.text: Hov1 has the most spots on Top Songs Sweden. “Förr nu & forever” is the highest at #10.
“Camera” by Ed Sheeran is the highest new entry on Top Songs Sweden at #33.
“Babblarnas vaggvisa” by Babblarna has been on Top Songs Sweden the longest, at 351 weeks straight.
“Superman” by Bolaget and HOFFMAESTRO is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Sweden, up 78 spots at #109.
